ews|title=The FP Power Map: The 500 most powerful people on the planet|url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2013/04/29/the_500_most_powerful_people_in_the_world|newspaper=Foreign Policy|date=May–June 2013|accessdate=2015-02-23|archive-date=2014-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409093019/http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2013/04/29/the_500_most_powerful_people_in_the_world|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

